## Development Workflow

### Issue Pipeline

Issues are tracked in `issues/INBOX.md`. The workflow:

1. Add raw bullets to `issues/INBOX.md`
2. Run triage (`$triage`) to create structured issue files
3. Run issue-review (`$issue-review <path>`) to add codebase context (3 parallel agents)
4. Run issue-advance (`$issue-advance <path>`) to convert reviewed issues into conductor tracks
5. Implement via conductor track workflow (TDD, phase checkpoints)
6. Run UAT (`$uat-create` then `$uat-run`) to validate completed tracks
7. Any UAT failures go back to INBOX as new issues

