## Codex-Specific Notes

- Multi-agent skills require `features.multi_agent = true` in config.toml
- Hooks are experimental (`codex_hooks = true`): SessionStart, PreToolUse, PostToolUse, UserPromptSubmit, Stop
- Agent spawning is explicit — ask for agents by name when needed
- Memory is manual via this file — no auto-memory system
